text: Nastassia Puzakova at the 2015 European Team Championships Super League Nastassia Puzakova (born 12 December 1993) is a Belarusian steeplechase runner. She competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the women's 3000 metres steeplechase race; her time of 10:14.08 in the heats did not qualify her for the final. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Belarusian female steeplechase runners Category:Olympic athletes of Belarus Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2016 Summer Olympics
